---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Projects | William Li" description="Selected projects and work samples.">
  <section>
    <h1>Projects</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="compact">
    <article>
      <p><b>Consult Your Community Website</b></p>
      <p>
        Organization website from scratch, with Next.js, React, Tailwind CSS, GitHub Actions, and Vercel.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <p><b>CLI-LLM</b></p>
      <p>
        Model-agnostic terminal interface for LLM inference. Built on Ink, React.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <p><b>Networking Protocols</b></p>
      <p>
        Traceroute, distance-vector protocol routing, and TCP/IP packet transportation.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <p><b>Employment Tracker</b></p>
      <p>
        CLI tool for tracking job applications. Supports multiple resumes, updates, and data analytics.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <p><b>UFO Sightings</b></p>
      <p>
        Data science + ML with Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib, and a web app built on Flask.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <hr />
  <section>
    <br>
    <p>
      "The human brain is a wonderful thing. It starts working the moment you are born, and never stops until you initialize a new git repository."
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
